{"tid":1865791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【左膠幾時死全家】社區組織協會：病人福祉因罷工無辜受害","createTime":"2020-02-06T11:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:25:49.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f828fc6db189bfba31330c669477cd4785db87f8","tid":1865791,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社區組織協會認為醫管局員工陣線的罷工持續，令病人福祉無辜受害。協會指，有接受過心導管手術的病人因醫護人手不足而延遲覆診及取藥。<br />\n<br />\n協會指，絕非站在道德高地，批評及指責罷工的醫護人員造成公營服務停擺。出席記者會的護理專科學院院長黃金月指，過去兩天收到40名護士報名到醫管局擔任兼職工作，但強調遠遠不足維持服務。"},{"pid":"45a1d5f7c0d6621cc0dff88b8bc241454cde6187","tid":1865791,"uid":13653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"咁前線醫護嘅福祉就可以犧牲了嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c919c84632a2c87cd2636f21d97439374aab8bf","tid":1865791,"uid":161125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"醫護就唔無辜？"},{"pid":"6cc36c8265983fe1e30d5f23e630a97e847a640a","tid":1865791,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係左膠 好似係親共派"},{"pid":"bc7c537a46a263b51a597c2abc877c8cbd9b3c25","tid":1865791,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"醫護安危因林鄭無辜受害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8201890427bd67baea40dc81c69af7731865d0ae","tid":1865791,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母施麗珊"},{"pid":"8c3e12c1b38d696082090add29118f7802e9310b","tid":1865791,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"你自己冇保護裝上前線送死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0328f0188b2bb0942c65705e5958c58090d83925","tid":1865791,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"<span sty